Name: Seasalt Popcorn
AttributesDescription: Grants 10% Healing Bonus to all Resonators in the team and increases their Max HP by 20%, lasting for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription: Seasalt Popcorn, your must-have snack for any Agon. Salty, joyful, and healthy! Every bite brings the taste of the sea.
